content: BBC1 et ITV1 continuent de s'affronter avec leurs divertissements du samedi. Hier, débutait une nouvelle confrontation entre #TheVoiceUK sur ITV1 (5.3 millions) et la nouveauté #TheGreatestDancer sur BBC1 (4.6 millions).
#thevoiceuk #thevoice Une bande annonce façon concert pour THE VOICE UK 8

Still in your pyjamas? Chill out and watch all of last night's amazing performances now - who would you have turned your chair for? https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLq6vSxwqHE1Gi86RBfrLEiaMNjNehQDC7 … #TheVoiceUK

Tom Jones singing ‘I’ll never fall in love again’ impromptu with Lonnie Donegan’s son is probably the greatest moment ever on #TheVoiceUK but it still doesn’t come close to Tony Angelino’s performance at the Down by the Riverside Club

A singing show on ITV beating a Dancing Show on the BBC for the first time in like 10 years and which one belongs to Simon Cowell now? LOL #TheVoiceUK #GreatestDancer
Ratings. #TheVoiceUK beat BBC1's dance show #TheGreatestDancer last night - 5.3m to 4.6m.  I have a feeling that receptionist will be checking the Office Angels website again soon.
